These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, iced-tea, water, milk
1. Beverage:iced-tea is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:milk is between Beverage:7up and Beverage:iced-tea##2
3. Beverage:milk is on the right of Beverage:7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | 7up | milk | iced-tea | water |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: 7up, mirinda, milk, soy-milk
1. Beverage:7up is on the left of Beverage:soy-milk##1
2. Beverage:mirinda is in an odd position##4
3. Beverage:mirinda is on the left or right of Beverage:7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | 7up | soy-milk | milk |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
