1. Music-Genre:dubstep is on the left or right of Music-Genre:house##3
2. Music-Genre:soul is in an even position##4
3. Music-Genre:funk is between Music-Genre:house and Music-Genre:soul##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | house | funk | soul |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
