3. Music-Genre:country is on the left or right of Music-Genre:indie##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | folk | techno | indie | country |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
