.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
City: liverpool, edinburgh, marseilles, venice
1. City:edinburgh == City:edinburgh##1
2. City:venice is on the left or right of City:marseilles##3
3. City:marseilles is on the far left or far right##3
4. City:liverpool is in an even position##4
5. City:venice is on the left of City:edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| City   | marseilles | venice | edinburgh | liverpool |

